{"TopicId":217271,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"What\u0027s the point of this forum?","CreatedByName":"Mantarochen","CreatedById":225270,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-20T00:03:07Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Mantarochen","CreatedById":225270,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-20T00:03:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust glancing over the threads, what is the purpose of this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEvery thread that has discussions about \u0022what the hell\u0022 is going on with the development of this game gets locked, moved, merged or just disappears.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you want feedback and feedback alone, just close the \u0022discussion\u0022 tab entirely and just keep the bug report section open.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do believe that pointing out that the game has sub 200 players at times is nothing a thread should get locked over. It sadly is the truth of the current state the game is in.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd I understand everyone that feels the need to express their sorrow and yes, maybe even some salt about spending $50 on a game, that seems to have little to none development happening on.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt least these threads could be a place for senior DEV staff to share some insights. Every other news channel of yours is basically dead, with no updates or insights other than\u0022 we are on it\u0022 to speak of.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich is quite sad, considering how the DEV staff propagated them being very communicative before the launch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starhawk","CreatedById":131400,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-20T00:13:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSince this is about the forum rather than the game itself it has been moved from KSP2 Discussion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HebaruSan","CreatedById":156657,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-20T00:58:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224285143\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217271\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221684540987\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225270\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mantarochen\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/19/2023 at 7:03 PM, Mantarochen said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust glancing over the threads, what is the purpose of this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDiscussion about games in the KSP franchise and related topics.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224285143\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217271\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221684540987\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225270\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mantarochen\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/19/2023 at 7:03 PM, Mantarochen said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmoved, merged\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s just the moderators keeping things tidy and well-organized. It\u0027s one of the nicer things about this place that you don\u0027t have to scroll through fifty duplicate threads posted to the wrong sub-forum to find the content that you\u0027re looking for, outside of the Science \u0026amp; Spaceflight subforum.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224285143\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022217271\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221684540987\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225270\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mantarochen\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/19/2023 at 7:03 PM, Mantarochen said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do believe that pointing out that the game has sub 200 players at times is nothing a thread should get locked over.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe moderators seem to agree, as the stated reason for locking those threads was the ceaseless pointless bickering between forum users, not the fact that player numbers were pointed out.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-05-25T18:07:59Z\u0022 title=\u002205/25/2023 06:07  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMay 25, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by HebaruSan\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-05-20T01:47:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#1b1e1f;color:#c9c5be;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003EEvery thread that has discussions about \u0022what the hell\u0022 is going on with the development of this game gets locked, moved, merged or just disappears.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\